Oracle Memory Uitilization script shows you the amount of memory resources used by Oracle database(s) on a server
for every ORACLE_HOME located on it.

Example:

$ ./omemutil.sh

*** Oracle memory utilization ***

**************************************************
$ORACLE_HOME=/u01/app/oracle/product/11.2/db_1

orcl            3134.92 Mb
chicago         1105.25 Mb
boston          10303.5 Mb
                ----------
Total:          14641 Mb
